  <entry>
    <title><![CDATA[如何搭建 Hexo 博客]]></title>
    <link href="https://zzh1991.github.io/2017/01/26/hello-world/"/>
    <id>https://zzh1991.github.io/2017/01/26/hello-world/</id>
    <published>2017-01-26T15:59:59.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-03-15T14:12:14.000Z</updated>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="先决条件"><a href="#先决条件" class="headerlink" title="先决条件"></a>先决条件</h2><ul>
<li>安装 git 和 node.js</li>
<li>新建 hexo 文件夹</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="搭建-hexo-环境"><a href="#搭建-hexo-环境" class="headerlink" title="搭建 hexo 环境"></a>搭建 hexo 环境</h2><ul>
<li>git bash: npm install hexo –no-optional</li>
<li>配置 git 环境下的 github</li>
<li>修改 _config.yml 文件中的 deployment</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">hexo init</div><div class="line">npm install</div><div class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</div><div class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="string">"邮箱地址"</span></div><div class="line">ssh-agent <span class="_">-s</span></div><div class="line"><span class="built_in">eval</span> `ssh-agent <span class="_">-s</span>`</div><div class="line">ssh-add</div><div class="line">&lt;!-- clip &lt; ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub --&gt;</div><div class="line">ssh -T git@github.com</div><div class="line">git config --global user.name <span class="string">"用户名"</span>  </div><div class="line">git config --global user.email “邮箱”</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">deploy:</div><div class="line">  <span class="built_in">type</span>: git</div><div class="line">  repo: &lt;repository github url&gt;</div><div class="line">  branch: [master]</div><div class="line">  message: [commit message]</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">hexo generate -&gt; hexo g</div><div class="line">hexo deploy   -&gt; hexo d</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="使用技巧"><a href="#使用技巧" class="headerlink" title="使用技巧"></a>使用技巧</h2><h3 id="新建博客文章"><a href="#新建博客文章" class="headerlink" title="新建博客文章"></a>新建博客文章</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">hexo new <span class="string">"paper name"</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="新建草稿"><a href="#新建草稿" class="headerlink" title="新建草稿"></a>新建草稿</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">hexo new draft <span class="string">"paper name"</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="增加头像"><a href="#增加头像" class="headerlink" title="增加头像"></a>增加头像</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">/theme/_config.yml</div><div class="line">avaster: <span class="string">"image source"</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="更改主题"><a href="#更改主题" class="headerlink" title="更改主题"></a>更改主题</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/MOxFIVE/hexo-theme-yelee.git themes/yelee</div><div class="line">theme: yelee</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="加入-README-md"><a href="#加入-README-md" class="headerlink" title="加入 README.md"></a>加入 README.md</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">skip_render:</div><div class="line">  - README.md</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="添加音乐"><a href="#添加音乐" class="headerlink" title="添加音乐"></a>添加音乐</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;center&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;iframe frameborder=&quot;no&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; marginwidth=&quot;0&quot; marginheight=&quot;0&quot; width=330 height=86 src=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;/center&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="Mac-安装-Hexo"><a href="#Mac-安装-Hexo" class="headerlink" title="Mac 安装 Hexo"></a>Mac 安装 Hexo</h2><h3 id="配置-git"><a href="#配置-git" class="headerlink" title="配置 git"></a>配置 git</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="string">"邮箱地址"</span></div><div class="line">pbcopy &lt; ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub</div><div class="line"><span class="comment"># add to GitHub SSH Key</span></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">ssh -T git@github.com</div><div class="line">git config --global user.name <span class="string">"用户名"</span>  </div><div class="line">git config --global user.email “邮箱”</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="安装-hexo"><a href="#安装-hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装 hexo"></a>安装 hexo</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli --no-optional</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> ~/Document/hexo</div><div class="line">hexo init</div><div class="line">npm install</div><div class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="comment"># modify the top _config.yaml</span></div><div class="line">deploy:</div><div class="line">  <span class="built_in">type</span>: git</div><div class="line">  repository: https://github.com/*/*.github.io.git</div><div class="line">  branch: master</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="comment"># every time</span></div><div class="line">hexo clean</div><div class="line">hexo generate</div><div class="line">hexo deploy</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
